entry.title: WEATHER ADVISORY , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 10:07 AM EST Saturday 04 February 2023

entry.title: Saturday: Flurries at times heavy or snow squalls. High minus 5.
entry.summary: Flurries at times heavy and local snow squalls. Local blowing snow. Amount 5 to 10 cm. Wind southwest 40 km/h gusting to 60. High minus 5. Wind chill minus 19 this morning and minus 12 this afternoon. Forecast issued 10:04 AM EST Saturday 04 February 2023

entry.title: Saturday night: Periods of snow. Low minus 9.
